=Trace Manager=

'''Basic Requirement integrates with Capella's Trace Manager'''. Requirements can also be applied on Capella elements using the Trace Manager.

Right-click on an element and select Wizards > Trace Manager


<center>[[Image:../Images/trace_menu.png]]</center>


From here you apply or remove requirements, by creating or deleting a requirement trace to the chosen requirements.


